OL,3,CCreator of Super Size Me, Morgan
OL,4,CSpurlock, dies aged 53
OL,6,FFilmmaker Morgan Spurlock, whose
OL,7,Fdocumentary Super Size Me helped shine
OL,8,Fan increased light on the
OL,9,Funhealthiness of the fast-food
OL,10,Findustry, has died aged 53.
OL,12,FSpurlock died on Thursday in New York
OL,13,Ffrom complications of cancer,
OL,14,Faccording to a statement issued Friday
OL,15,Fby his family.
OL,17,FHis brother, Craig Spurlock, said in a
OL,18,Fstatement: "It was a sad day, as we
OL,19,Fsaid goodbye to my brother Morgan.
