OL,3,CCreator of Super Size Me, Morgan
OL,4,CSpurlock, dies aged 53
OL,6,F"Morgan gave so much through his art,
OL,7,Fideas, and generosity.
OL,9,F"The world has lost a true creative
OL,10,Fgenius and a special man. I am so
OL,11,Fproud to have worked together with
OL,12,Fhim."
OL,14,FSpurlock's 2004 documentary Super Size
OL,15,FMe shone a light on the dominance of
OL,16,Fthe fast food industry in the United
OL,17,FStates and the impact it had on
OL,18,Fobesity, diabetes and other major
OL,19,Fillnesses.
