OL,3,CCreator of Super Size Me, Morgan
OL,4,CSpurlock, dies aged 53
OL,6,FThe documentary saw Spurlock eating
OL,7,Ffast food every day for a month and
OL,8,Frecording the impact on his body.
OL,10,FThe impact of the documentary led to
OL,11,FMcDonald's discontinuing its supersize
OL,12,Fportions.
OL,14,FIt also saw fast-food chains and
OL,15,Frestaurants stressing freshness,
OL,16,Fartisanal methods, farm-to-table
OL,17,Fgoodness and ethically sourced
OL,18,Fingredients. But nutritionally not
OL,19,Fmuch has changed.
