OL,6,FHe returned with a sequel in 2019
OL,7,FSuper Size Me 2: Holy Chicken! - a
OL,8,Flook at an industry that processes
OL,9,Fnine billion animals a year in America.
OL,11,FSpeaking in 2019 he said: "There has
OL,12,Fbeen this massive shift and people say
OL,13,Fto me, 'so has the food gotten
OL,14,Fhealthier?' And I say, 'Well, the
OL,15,Fmarketing sure has'."
